From: STGR Browser Team <dev@stgr-browser.dev>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Enhanced tab search with fuzzy matching, URL search, and keyboard navigation

Upgrades the vertical tabs search box with:
- Fuzzy matching (type non-contiguous characters, e.g. "gthb" matches "GitHub")
- URL search (searches page URL in addition to tab title)
- Match highlighting (matched characters are wrapped in <span> with underline)
- Keyboard navigation (up/down arrows cycle through filtered results, Enter selects)
- Search result count badge ("3 of 12 tabs")
- Quick switch mode (Ctrl+P anywhere in sidebar focuses the search box)
- Clear button on the search field when input is present
- Search icon (magnifying glass) at the start of the search field
- Visual active state on the search header when filtering is active
- Preferences for fuzzy matching and URL search toggles

